~ start
if !GameFlags.check_elevator(ID)
	do GameFlags.unlock_elevator(ID)
	do AudioManager.play_jingle("elevatorChime")
	Discovered Elevator [color=a7a5ff]{{ID}}[/color]!
Ride the elevator?
- Ride => elevatorEnter
- Do not
=> END

~ elevatorEnter
do enter_elevator()
=> END

~ creator
???: Welcome to my elevator room.
???: I, am the creator of the elevator.
???: With my glorious creation, I may travel the world at my leisure.
???: Please try out my elevator when you have a chance.